      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GO ZIPPER GO (5) looks close to another win after hitting the frame in a one length second (22.75) in a Grade 5 at this track. Rates highly and will give a great sight. FUGENZO (7) had been in super honest form hitting the frame three times on end before finishing fourth (30.43) at Richmond last time. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of three starts. The form out of last race has been strong. Warrants plenty of respect. RUPEE'S GALORE (1) looks close to another win after finishing third from Box 1 last time (22.98) at Maitland. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Must be included in calculations. NIGHT WORKS (2) is another with top-three prospects.",
